# Liquid Obsidian Design System

## Color Palette (CSS Variables ‚Äî ALWAYS use these, never raw hex)
### Backgrounds
- `--color-obsidian: #131313` ‚Äî page background
- `--color-midnight: #1c1b1b` ‚Äî card backgrounds (inactive)
- `--color-deep-void: #0e0e0e` ‚Äî input backgrounds, deepest surfaces

### Gold (use sparingly ‚Äî reserved for importance)
- `--color-gold-rare: #f2ca50` ‚Äî ONLY for: current player, primary CTA, active turn, critical moments
- `--color-gold-support: #d4af37` ‚Äî dimmed icons, hover states, secondary gold

### Surfaces
- `--surface-container: #201f1f` ‚Äî low-emphasis containers
- `--surface-high: #2a2a2a` ‚Äî elevated cards, active panels
- `--surface-highest: #353534` ‚Äî modal overlays, dropdowns
- `--surface-bright: #3a3939` ‚Äî highest emphasis surface
- `--outline-variant: #4d4635` ‚Äî subtle borders, dividers
- `--outline: #99907c` ‚Äî secondary text, labels, inactive elements

### Atmosphere (phase-dependent accents)
- `--atmosphere-exploration: #1b4d6e`
- `--atmosphere-combat: #8b2500`
- `--atmosphere-mystery: #7b2d8e`
- `--atmosphere-social: #b8860b`

### Text
- `--color-silver-muted: #e5e2e1` ‚Äî primary body text
- `--color-silver-dim: #d0c5af` ‚Äî secondary text, taglines

### Status
- `--color-success: #4ade80`
- `--color-failure: #ffb3ad`
- `--color-critical: #7b2d8e`
- `--color-error: #ef4444`

### Glass
- `--glass-bg: rgba(28,27,27,0.7)` ‚Äî standard glass
- `--glass-bg-heavy: rgba(28,27,27,0.88)` ‚Äî heavy glass (bottom sheets, overlays)
- `--glass-blur: 12px`
- `--glass-edge-glow: 0 0 20px rgba(242,202,80,0.15)`

## Typography
| Class | Font | Use For |
|-------|------|---------|
| `.text-fantasy` | Noto Serif (serif) | Lore text, titles, character names, headings (class name is historical ‚Äî not a genre default) |
| default (Manrope) | sans-serif | Gameplay text, UI labels, body copy |
| `.text-data` | Inter (mono-like) | HP numbers, dice values, stats, numerical data |

## Utility Classes (defined in `globals.css`)
- `.glass` ‚Äî standard glass surface (blur + border + shadow)
- `.glass-heavy` ‚Äî heavy glass (bottom sheets, overlays)
- `.glow-gold` ‚Äî gold edge glow
- `.metallic-edge` ‚Äî subtle metallic border
- `.selected-glow` ‚Äî active selection glow (gold pulsing border)
- `.gradient-hp` ‚Äî HP bar gradient (red)
- `.gradient-mana` ‚Äî mana bar gradient (gold)
- `.scrollbar-hide` ‚Äî hides scrollbar

## Animation Classes
- `.animate-breathe` ‚Äî subtle scale pulse (3s)
- `.animate-pulse-glow` ‚Äî gold glow pulse (2s)
- `.animate-gold-breathe-glow` ‚Äî breathing gold box-shadow (2.6s)
- `.animate-shimmer` ‚Äî loading shimmer effect
- `.animate-shake-once` ‚Äî error shake (0.4s)
- `.animate-fade-in` ‚Äî opacity 0->1 (0.3s)
- `.animate-slide-up` ‚Äî slide up + fade in (0.4s)
- `.animate-hp-flash-damage` ‚Äî red HP flash
- `.animate-hp-flash-heal` ‚Äî green HP flash

## Timing Variables
- `--duration-fast: 150ms` ‚Äî micro-interactions
- `--duration-med: 300ms` ‚Äî standard transitions
- `--duration-slow: 800ms` ‚Äî dramatic reveals
- `--ease-out-soft: cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)`
- `--ease-spring: cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1)`

## Spacing
- `--void-gap: 1.5rem` ‚Äî standard void gap between modules
- `--void-gap-lg: 2.5rem` ‚Äî large void gap between sections

## Border Radius
- `--radius-card: 4px` ‚Äî cards, containers
- `--radius-button: 4px` ‚Äî buttons
- `--radius-chip: 4px` ‚Äî chips, tags
- `--radius-pill: 9999px` ‚Äî pills, badges

## Component Catalog
| Component | File | When to Use |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| `GoldButton` | `ui/gold-button.tsx` | Primary CTA, important actions |
| `GhostButton` | `ui/ghost-button.tsx` | Secondary actions, cancel, back |
| `GlassCard` | `ui/glass-card.tsx` | Card surfaces, info panels |
| `PillSelect` | `ui/pill-select.tsx` | Enum/option selection (campaign mode, party size) |
| `BottomSheet` | `sheets/bottom-sheet.tsx` | Slide-up panels (character sheet, journal, party) |
| `LoadingSkeleton` | `ui/loading-skeleton.tsx` | Loading states |
| `ConnectionStatus` | `ui/connection-status.tsx` | Pusher connection indicator |
| `Toast` | `ui/toast.tsx` | Notifications, errors, success messages |

## Layout Rules
- Void gaps between modules: `gap-[var(--void-gap)]` or `gap-[var(--void-gap-lg)]`
- No tab navigation during active gameplay ‚Äî use bottom sheets
- Thumb-first: interactive elements in bottom 30% of screen
- `min-h-dvh` not `min-h-screen`
- Max content width: `max-w-md` (448px) for main content area
- Mobile-first: design for mobile, responsive up

## Motion Rules
- Use Framer Motion `<motion.div>` with `initial`/`animate`/`exit` for enter/exit
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` ‚Äî already handled in `globals.css`
- Subtle, breathing, selective ‚Äî no overanimation
- Gold surfaces breathe; cold surfaces are static
